### 1. Create Order with localized product names
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/order/Orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "Khách Hàng Quốc Tế",
  "items": [
    {
      "sku": "SKU-RED",
      "name": "Red T-Shirt",
      "qty": 2,
      "price": 20
    },
    {
      "sku": "SKU-VN",
      "name": "Áo Thun Màu Đỏ",
      "qty": 1,
      "price": 25
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Get list of OrderItems without setting Accept-Language
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/order/OrderItems
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get list of OrderItems with language EN (English / default)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/order/OrderItems
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: en

### 4. Get list of OrderItems with language VI (Vietnamese)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/order/OrderItems
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: vi

### 5. Check stock for SKU-RED
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/order/checkStock
Content-Type: application/json

{ "sku": "SKU-RED" }